WEBVTT

01:30.820 --> 01:34.990
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.350 --> 01:36.430
Our company's second-quarter

01:35.840 --> 01:39.380
[2015]

01:36.430 --> 01:37.310
top seller

01:37.840 --> 01:39.039
is our new colleague,

01:39.229 --> 01:39.960
Xia Xiaolan.

01:41.950 --> 01:43.640
Here's the certificate and bonus.

01:43.640 --> 01:44.400
Keep up the good work.

01:44.400 --> 01:45.000
Thank you.

01:45.000 --> 01:45.590
Everyone should

01:45.590 --> 01:47.000
learn from Xia Xiaolan in the future

01:47.000 --> 01:47.920
and create more value

01:47.920 --> 01:49.580
and benefits for our company.

01:50.229 --> 01:51.490
Liu, come to my office.

01:51.610 --> 01:54.200
[Ms. Xiaolan won the Top Seller title
in the Business Group's Q2 2015 sales ranking.]

01:53.000 --> 01:54.150
Anyone who gets her clients

01:54.150 --> 01:55.680
could become the top seller,

01:55.680 --> 01:56.200
right?

01:56.680 --> 01:58.200
Don't try to deny it.

01:58.710 --> 01:59.350
She goes

01:59.350 --> 02:01.070
to Mr. Gu's office every day.

02:01.170 --> 02:01.890
Who knows

02:01.920 --> 02:03.980
what kind of relationship they have?

02:14.630 --> 02:16.400
How do rumors start?

02:17.079 --> 02:18.120
Is it because of jealousy

02:18.120 --> 02:18.980
or just for fun—

02:19.470 --> 02:21.200
It is often impossible to know.

02:22.150 --> 02:22.910
But I know it.

02:23.870 --> 02:25.670
Running away won't stop rumors.

02:26.310 --> 02:27.079
Backing down

02:27.710 --> 02:30.000
will only be seen
as an admission of guilt.

02:30.000 --> 02:31.800
People will embellish the story

02:31.960 --> 02:33.090
with vivid details.

02:34.210 --> 02:38.370
[Episode 2: Rumors That Grew Wings]

02:40.280 --> 02:40.680
Come here.

02:40.680 --> 02:42.150
You think we don't know
who you really are?

02:42.150 --> 02:42.750
Let me go!

02:43.240 --> 02:43.800
Help!

02:43.800 --> 02:44.520
Weren't you getting along

02:44.520 --> 02:45.590
well with Zhang Erlai?

02:45.590 --> 02:46.120
Let me go!

02:46.120 --> 02:47.710
Why are you pretending to be pure?

02:47.710 --> 02:49.630
Everyone knows you're Xia Xiaolan

02:49.630 --> 02:51.760
from Dahe Village, who sleeps around.

03:00.430 --> 03:01.160
Are you okay?

03:05.030 --> 03:06.560
You guys are really something—

03:06.560 --> 03:08.310
bullying a girl in broad daylight.

03:08.310 --> 03:08.910
Get him!

03:24.680 --> 03:25.140
Come on.

03:25.200 --> 03:25.630
Excuse me.

03:25.630 --> 03:26.360
Move aside.

03:27.870 --> 03:28.600
Does it hurt?

03:28.910 --> 03:29.430
Yes.

03:30.680 --> 03:31.430
Want to keep fighting?

03:31.430 --> 03:31.870
No.

03:32.240 --> 03:32.590
No. No.

03:32.590 --> 03:33.150
Stop it!

03:34.520 --> 03:35.430
What's going on here?

03:35.430 --> 03:36.000
Officer.

03:36.110 --> 03:36.870
It's them.

03:38.430 --> 03:39.230
Take them all.

03:39.470 --> 03:39.960
Get up.

03:40.060 --> 03:40.520
Come on.

03:40.680 --> 03:41.800
Get up. Get up.

03:41.910 --> 03:42.570
Easy, easy.

03:42.590 --> 03:43.450
-Ouch.
-Get up.

03:45.130 --> 03:45.750
And you two,

03:45.750 --> 03:47.280
come with us to the station.

03:47.590 --> 03:48.400
Cheng, are you okay?

03:48.400 --> 03:48.930
I'm fine.

03:56.410 --> 03:57.340
Are you alright?

04:05.660 --> 04:07.270
Alright,
we've understood the situation already.

04:07.270 --> 04:08.130
You can go back.

04:08.710 --> 04:10.400
Miss,
when walking alone on remote paths,

04:10.400 --> 04:11.790
you should be more careful.

04:11.790 --> 04:13.470
Xia Xiaolan is just a loose woman,

04:13.470 --> 04:14.750
not some good girl.

04:14.960 --> 04:15.750
Shut up.

04:17.709 --> 04:18.910
Okay, you can go back.

04:19.360 --> 04:19.820
Thank you.

04:19.820 --> 04:20.420
Thank you.

04:23.430 --> 04:24.430
Thank you so much.

04:24.830 --> 04:25.760
That's alright.

04:26.270 --> 04:28.270
Do you have somewhere else to go?

04:30.590 --> 04:31.120
Yes.

04:41.100 --> 04:41.710
Miss.

04:42.430 --> 04:43.830
What are you looking for?

04:43.870 --> 04:44.920
Is it a wall clock

04:45.120 --> 04:46.190
or a wristwatch?

04:46.390 --> 04:47.120
Alarm clock.

04:47.310 --> 04:48.159
Do you have an alarm clock?

04:48.159 --> 04:49.560
Yes, yes. Look over here.

04:54.750 --> 04:57.150
There aren't any
with cartoon prints here.

04:57.390 --> 04:59.320
This is the only one with a pattern.

05:00.830 --> 05:01.890
Let me see this one.

05:02.000 --> 05:02.480
Sure.

05:05.240 --> 05:05.900
Take a look.

05:08.030 --> 05:09.030
Are you buying it?

05:09.190 --> 05:11.190
Don't touch it if you're not buying.

05:12.360 --> 05:12.800
Okay.

05:13.000 --> 05:14.060
I'll take this one.

05:23.750 --> 05:24.610
Have you got it?

05:25.800 --> 05:26.630
You helped me today.

05:26.630 --> 05:27.230
Thank you.

05:27.510 --> 05:28.440
That's alright.

05:28.720 --> 05:29.920
My name is Zhou Cheng.

05:29.920 --> 05:31.000
I am a high school graduate.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.680
I'll start working in two months.

05:32.680 --> 05:33.870
I've been free lately,

05:33.870 --> 05:35.100
so I've been doing some transport work.

05:35.100 --> 05:36.030
But don't worry.

05:36.220 --> 05:37.480
It's legitimate work.

05:37.750 --> 05:39.210
I just make a small profit.

05:40.000 --> 05:40.600
Now,

05:41.750 --> 05:42.880
may I get to know you?

05:45.800 --> 05:47.060
My name is Xia Xiaolan.

05:47.480 --> 05:48.680
As for anything else,

05:49.040 --> 05:50.240
I don't know, either.

05:51.159 --> 05:52.690
You're quite interesting,

05:52.800 --> 05:54.659
not even knowing about yourself.

05:57.750 --> 05:58.480
Xia Xiaolan.

06:03.720 --> 06:04.450
Xia Xiaolan!

06:05.800 --> 06:06.630
Ms. Xiaolan.

06:07.680 --> 06:08.560
Ms. Xiaolan.

06:10.020 --> 06:10.770
Ms. Xiaolan.

06:15.160 --> 06:15.890
Ms. Xiaolan.

06:17.830 --> 06:19.040
You're finally awake.

06:19.040 --> 06:20.970
You just fainted from heatstroke.

06:21.310 --> 06:21.640
Here.

06:23.770 --> 06:24.800
This is my own water bottle.

06:24.800 --> 06:25.580
I've washed it three times.

06:25.580 --> 06:26.510
It's very clean.

06:27.040 --> 06:28.390
Have some water to recover.

06:28.390 --> 06:28.720
Here.

06:34.510 --> 06:35.600
You are...

06:37.000 --> 06:38.000
Wang...

06:38.430 --> 06:39.560
Wang Jianhua.

06:40.159 --> 06:41.270
I'm from Beijing,

06:41.480 --> 06:42.159
responsible for promoting

06:42.159 --> 06:44.420
our agricultural planting techniques.

06:45.480 --> 06:47.210
I don't understand any of that.

06:47.830 --> 06:48.800
So you're just someone

06:48.800 --> 06:50.200
who farms with us, right?

06:50.890 --> 06:52.330
Right, that's not wrong.

06:53.070 --> 06:53.800
Thank you.

06:55.600 --> 06:56.360
Take it easy.

07:01.070 --> 07:02.400
That's enough. Thanks.

07:02.560 --> 07:03.070
No, no.

07:03.630 --> 07:04.750
Your heatstroke was serious.

07:04.750 --> 07:06.350
You should rest a bit longer.

07:07.310 --> 07:08.680
Everyone, stop crowding around.

07:08.680 --> 07:09.610
Get back to work.

07:11.920 --> 07:13.380
Have another sip of water.

07:13.560 --> 07:14.490
Drink some more.

07:15.360 --> 07:15.960
Thank you.

07:31.760 --> 07:32.820
Where am I?

07:33.120 --> 07:33.780
Don't move.

07:33.830 --> 07:35.030
You're still on an IV.

07:40.040 --> 07:41.040
Did I fall asleep?

07:42.120 --> 07:42.600
Yes.

07:44.000 --> 07:45.460
You seemed to be dreaming.

07:45.560 --> 07:47.070
You were smiling in your sleep.

07:47.070 --> 07:47.930
Just like this.

07:50.300 --> 07:52.200
Everyone else has dreams

07:52.390 --> 07:53.830
with happy and joyful smiles.

07:53.830 --> 07:56.490
Why did it seem like
you were mocking something?

07:58.159 --> 07:59.070
I dreamed of

07:59.070 --> 08:00.630
a hasty love story.

08:01.800 --> 08:02.430
You know, people

08:02.430 --> 08:04.430
are really interesting sometimes.

08:05.190 --> 08:06.850
They meet someone a few times,

08:07.000 --> 08:08.430
get a little bit of care,

08:09.070 --> 08:12.040
and then they want to spend
the rest of their lives with them.

08:12.040 --> 08:13.720
This standard for choosing a partner

08:13.720 --> 08:15.000
is really quite low.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.310
So,

08:20.240 --> 08:22.120
you don't believe in love at first sight.

08:22.120 --> 08:23.380
How can you fall in love

08:23.510 --> 08:25.310
when you know nothing about them?

08:25.310 --> 08:27.370
What if the attraction at first sight

08:28.120 --> 08:29.120
is strong enough?

08:31.240 --> 08:32.240
What attraction—

08:33.200 --> 08:34.200
strong enough

08:34.870 --> 08:36.120
to suck my blood?

08:38.000 --> 08:39.860
Nurse, please remove the IV here.

08:40.390 --> 08:41.600
Okay, coming.

08:46.750 --> 08:47.550
Press here.

08:50.080 --> 08:50.480
Okay.

08:52.750 --> 08:53.350
Thank you.

08:54.480 --> 08:55.550
Take it easy.

08:56.120 --> 08:56.550
Come.

09:02.550 --> 09:03.120
Um,

09:03.550 --> 09:05.010
let me take you home later.

09:05.320 --> 09:06.320
Don't refuse yet.

09:07.600 --> 09:08.240
If you insist

09:08.240 --> 09:09.370
on going back alone,

09:09.510 --> 09:11.310
I'll still insist on taking you.

09:11.600 --> 09:12.270
Warm,

09:13.240 --> 09:14.200
considerate,

09:14.840 --> 09:16.030
knows his boundaries—

09:16.030 --> 09:16.790
This boy

09:16.790 --> 09:18.320
actually matches my taste.

09:18.750 --> 09:20.390
But I don't believe a man's feelings

09:20.390 --> 09:22.320
can stay focused on just one woman,

09:22.440 --> 09:24.000
especially when she's

09:24.030 --> 09:25.320
over 10 years older than him

09:25.320 --> 09:26.920
and from another dimension.

09:28.960 --> 09:29.560
Thank you.

09:37.150 --> 09:38.480
What kind of trash

09:38.480 --> 09:40.000
is gossiping
about other people's business,

09:40.000 --> 09:40.480
saying—

09:42.000 --> 09:42.510
Fen.

09:43.120 --> 09:44.450
Go ahead with your work.

09:48.360 --> 09:49.220
What happened?

09:49.550 --> 09:50.510
Just now, on my way here,

09:50.510 --> 09:52.170
I overheard two people saying

09:52.630 --> 09:53.390
that our Xiaolan

09:53.390 --> 09:54.750
was bullied in town.

09:55.030 --> 09:56.960
They even called her a loose woman.

09:56.960 --> 09:57.760
Who said that?

09:59.150 --> 10:00.600
I chewed them both out.

10:01.790 --> 10:02.440
Don't worry.

10:02.440 --> 10:03.480
As long as I'm around,

10:03.480 --> 10:05.870
no one in the village will dare
to gossip anymore.

10:05.870 --> 10:06.550
However,

10:07.000 --> 10:08.380
I can't control what happens elsewhere.

10:08.380 --> 10:09.710
Alright, I understand.

10:10.480 --> 10:11.080
You should

10:11.440 --> 10:12.550
go check on Fen first.

10:12.550 --> 10:13.480
I'll go meet Xiaolan.

10:13.480 --> 10:13.810
Okay.

10:22.120 --> 10:24.240
Just turn the corner ahead
and we're there.

10:24.240 --> 10:24.840
Thank you.

10:26.120 --> 10:27.050
That's alright.

10:29.440 --> 10:30.040
Thank you.

10:30.510 --> 10:30.960
Cheng,

10:31.630 --> 10:32.670
I'll sort the goods.

10:32.670 --> 10:33.400
You two talk.

10:40.150 --> 10:40.910
Wei and I

10:41.030 --> 10:42.720
are staying at the Anqing Guesthouse.

10:42.720 --> 10:43.360
If you're going

10:43.360 --> 10:44.720
to the town again tomorrow,

10:44.720 --> 10:46.250
you can ask us to go with you.

10:46.600 --> 10:47.150
No need.

10:47.390 --> 10:47.910
Thanks.

10:48.120 --> 10:48.650
Gotta go.

11:14.600 --> 11:15.320
Thank you.

11:16.840 --> 11:17.370
Xiaolan!

11:24.630 --> 11:25.320
Who are you?

11:26.200 --> 11:27.660
Why are you following her?

11:28.000 --> 11:29.480
Hello, I'm Zhou Cheng,

11:30.200 --> 11:31.440
and I'm the delivery person.

11:31.440 --> 11:32.510
He helped me today.

11:38.270 --> 11:39.470
Well, thank you then.

11:40.510 --> 11:42.150
You should go back and rest early.

11:42.150 --> 11:43.210
I'll be going then.

11:49.030 --> 11:50.290
Where are you staying?

11:51.750 --> 11:53.750
I'm staying at the town guesthouse.

11:54.600 --> 11:56.720
I happen to be going
to the town tomorrow.

11:56.720 --> 11:58.180
I'll bring you breakfast.

11:58.440 --> 11:59.080
And for lunch,

11:59.080 --> 12:00.810
I'll treat you to a meal in town—

12:00.820 --> 12:01.870
as thanks

12:02.240 --> 12:03.040
from Xiaolan.

12:04.440 --> 12:05.100
Go back now.

12:07.080 --> 12:07.680
Thank you.

12:14.510 --> 12:14.960
Cheng.

12:15.270 --> 12:16.000
Who was that guy just now?

12:16.000 --> 12:17.130
He seemed so fierce.

12:18.030 --> 12:19.230
Probably her father.

12:20.390 --> 12:20.960
Let's go.

12:21.360 --> 12:21.890
Let's go.

12:25.150 --> 12:26.130
He helped you.

12:26.200 --> 12:27.860
We should thank him properly.

12:28.270 --> 12:29.670
Homemade food

12:29.790 --> 12:30.790
shows sincerity.

12:31.720 --> 12:32.930
Tomorrow morning,

12:33.630 --> 12:35.630
I'll go to the police station in town

12:35.630 --> 12:37.360
to ask about today's incident.

12:37.390 --> 12:38.750
And I'll also check

12:39.120 --> 12:40.580
if they're decent people.

12:44.360 --> 12:44.910
Thank...

12:45.960 --> 12:46.670
Thank you.

12:47.870 --> 12:48.600
Kid...

12:49.200 --> 12:50.390
What are you thanking me for?

12:50.390 --> 12:51.190
We're family.

12:59.630 --> 13:01.030
Those two are city folks.

13:01.150 --> 13:03.000
I wonder

13:03.160 --> 13:03.910
if they will like

13:03.910 --> 13:04.960
these sour radish and pork dumplings.

13:04.960 --> 13:06.000
They've probably never had them before.

13:06.000 --> 13:07.530
Let them try something new.

13:09.020 --> 13:10.200
Cook their dumplings

13:10.200 --> 13:11.260
tomorrow morning.

13:11.600 --> 13:12.130
Alright.

13:12.200 --> 13:14.670
It's the New Year! Time to eat dumplings!

13:15.030 --> 13:16.790
Now we can have them
even when it's not the New Year.

13:16.790 --> 13:17.850
Life is better now.

13:18.870 --> 13:19.600
Thank you...

13:20.160 --> 13:22.090
Thank you so much for your trouble.

13:22.440 --> 13:24.200
Xiaolan, it's no trouble at all.

13:24.200 --> 13:26.070
We're making them for ourselves, too.

13:26.070 --> 13:27.120
Oh right, I remember

13:27.120 --> 13:28.630
you make the prettiest dumplings.

13:28.630 --> 13:29.440
You should

13:29.480 --> 13:30.030
make their dumplings.

13:30.030 --> 13:30.440
Yes.

13:30.480 --> 13:30.940
Come on.

13:31.440 --> 13:31.720
Yes.

13:31.960 --> 13:33.890
Xiaolan makes the best dumplings.

13:34.720 --> 13:35.240
Come on.

13:35.720 --> 13:36.320
Wrap one.

13:36.410 --> 13:37.680
I don't know how.

13:39.750 --> 13:41.480
The first batch is ready. Here.

13:41.720 --> 13:43.450
Try them and see how they taste.

13:43.790 --> 13:44.790
Try them quickly.

13:45.000 --> 13:46.530
Tao, let Xiaolan eat first.

13:46.720 --> 13:47.320
It's okay.

13:47.510 --> 13:48.310
Tao, go ahead.

13:49.120 --> 13:50.250
Thank you, Xiaolan.

13:50.290 --> 13:51.070
Hurry up.

13:51.120 --> 13:52.320
Be careful. It's hot.

13:53.480 --> 13:54.480
How does it taste?

14:01.240 --> 14:02.870
Even though the alarm clocks
are different,

14:02.870 --> 14:04.550
sincerity makes all the difference.

14:04.550 --> 14:05.960
Please, let me go back.

14:56.910 --> 14:57.600
Xiaolan.

14:58.550 --> 15:00.210
You set an alarm at night, too?

15:04.750 --> 15:05.600
I was just trying it out.

15:05.600 --> 15:06.240
Alright.

15:06.630 --> 15:08.150
Try it. Try it.

15:26.360 --> 15:27.030
Lan.

15:27.790 --> 15:29.250
Is the alarm clock broken?

15:29.360 --> 15:30.620
Let me get you a new one.

15:31.720 --> 15:32.320
It's fine.

15:32.790 --> 15:33.270
No need.

15:51.480 --> 15:51.940
What...

15:52.750 --> 15:53.510
What are you going to say?

15:53.510 --> 15:54.740
No… nothing.

15:55.150 --> 15:55.550
I...

15:56.150 --> 15:57.480
I'll get you some water.

16:05.790 --> 16:07.080
Useless thing.

16:15.320 --> 16:16.380
Stop making noise.

16:25.800 --> 16:27.600
What's wrong with Xiaolan?

16:28.870 --> 16:30.390
She's probably testing the alarm clock

16:30.390 --> 16:31.550
to see if it works.

16:31.960 --> 16:33.840
Why do we need alarm clocks here?

16:34.360 --> 16:35.840
When the sun rises and the roosters crow,

16:35.840 --> 16:36.840
everyone gets up.

16:37.080 --> 16:38.120
Whenever she wants to wake up,

16:38.120 --> 16:39.270
we can call her.

16:40.080 --> 16:40.750
Maybe

16:40.870 --> 16:42.600
she's afraid of troubling you.

16:44.360 --> 16:44.910
Fen.

16:45.200 --> 16:46.150
Have you noticed

16:46.840 --> 16:48.640
that since Xiaolan hit her head,

16:48.670 --> 16:50.320
she seems different from before?

16:50.320 --> 16:51.960
Look, she doesn't eat vinegar,

16:51.960 --> 16:53.420
doesn't drink spicy soup,

16:53.570 --> 16:55.210
can't even make dumplings,

16:55.630 --> 16:57.480
and she's so polite with us,

16:57.790 --> 16:59.590
like she's become someone else.

17:00.030 --> 17:00.720
Later,

17:01.120 --> 17:01.840
you should take her

17:01.840 --> 17:03.570
to the big hospital in the city.

17:32.240 --> 17:33.500
What's wrong with you?

17:33.550 --> 17:34.750
Are you crying again?

17:38.400 --> 17:39.200
It's nothing.

17:39.750 --> 17:41.310
I'm just happy to see

17:41.680 --> 17:42.720
you doing so well.

17:44.440 --> 17:45.240
Don't worry.

17:45.920 --> 17:47.830
I'm not the same Xia Xiaolan as before.

17:47.830 --> 17:49.760
I won't do foolish things anymore.

17:54.550 --> 17:55.350
I know.

17:57.590 --> 17:58.240
Xiaolan.

17:59.590 --> 18:00.480
Today I collected

18:00.480 --> 18:02.080
two big baskets of duck eggs.

18:03.270 --> 18:03.790
What?

18:05.240 --> 18:06.110
Didn't you tell me

18:06.110 --> 18:07.710
to collect duck eggs at home?

18:08.640 --> 18:09.640
At first,

18:09.640 --> 18:11.030
I didn't have much of a plan.

18:11.030 --> 18:12.030
Then I suddenly remembered

18:12.030 --> 18:12.830
what you said,

18:12.880 --> 18:14.610
"Just look for kids Tao's age."

18:14.960 --> 18:16.530
One minute, one kid would pop up here,

18:16.530 --> 18:17.160
holding one.

18:17.160 --> 18:18.240
The next minute,
another would pop up there,

18:18.240 --> 18:18.970
holding two.

18:19.480 --> 18:20.400
In just one afternoon,

18:20.400 --> 18:22.400
I collected two big baskets of duck eggs.

18:22.400 --> 18:22.960
Tomorrow I'll go with you

18:22.960 --> 18:24.030
to sell the eggs.

18:26.200 --> 18:26.680
No need.

18:27.920 --> 18:28.920
I'll go by myself tomorrow.

18:28.920 --> 18:30.250
You should rest at home.

18:33.440 --> 18:33.970
Alright.

18:34.840 --> 18:35.510
Your uncle will

18:35.510 --> 18:36.570
go with you anyway.

18:37.440 --> 18:39.510
I'll stay home and collect eggs.

18:42.480 --> 18:43.310
Although

18:43.790 --> 18:44.590
everything here

18:44.590 --> 18:45.720
feels strange to me.

18:47.550 --> 18:48.880
This woman named Liu Fen

18:49.560 --> 18:51.420
makes me want to get closer to her.

18:52.510 --> 18:53.710
She is simple-minded

18:53.880 --> 18:54.790
and weak,

18:55.880 --> 18:57.440
but she gives her all

18:57.920 --> 18:59.120
to love her daughter.

18:59.680 --> 19:00.480
Xia Xiaolan.

19:01.550 --> 19:03.160
I actually envy you a little.

19:21.350 --> 19:22.110
This kid

19:22.110 --> 19:24.110
is always playing
with new gadgets.

19:24.110 --> 19:25.440
This thing is loud.

19:47.510 --> 19:50.240
What time did I cross over?

19:52.330 --> 19:52.990
Afternoon.

19:53.510 --> 19:53.880
Yes.

19:54.720 --> 19:56.520
I'll try again in the afternoon.

19:58.070 --> 19:58.600
Brother.

19:59.240 --> 19:59.900
Dumplings.

20:00.030 --> 20:00.400
Okay.

20:00.510 --> 20:00.840
Here.

20:03.960 --> 20:04.550
Xiaolan.

20:05.270 --> 20:06.470
Hurry down. Let's go.

20:06.550 --> 20:07.790
Let's deliver these dumplings.

20:07.790 --> 20:08.270
Okay.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.720
Here comes the noodles.

20:16.880 --> 20:17.440
Thank you.

20:17.440 --> 20:18.370
That's alright.

20:20.790 --> 20:23.190
These dumplings are beautifully wrapped.

20:23.960 --> 20:26.350
My family made them.

20:26.480 --> 20:27.740
I'm not very good at it.

20:29.480 --> 20:30.550
I actually know how.

20:30.550 --> 20:31.880
I'll show you sometime.

20:34.960 --> 20:36.070
Wei was there yesterday.

20:36.070 --> 20:37.920
He went with your uncle
to the police station.

20:37.920 --> 20:39.250
It will be handled well.

20:39.750 --> 20:40.550
Thank you all.

20:40.750 --> 20:41.750
Don't mention it.

20:45.310 --> 20:46.750
What's in these dumplings?

20:46.750 --> 20:47.680
Pickled radish?

20:49.070 --> 20:49.670
It's good.

20:49.790 --> 20:51.590
This way, it's not greasy at all.

20:52.830 --> 20:54.890
Your family must be well-off, right?

20:55.080 --> 20:55.790
In these times,

20:55.790 --> 20:57.790
everyone loves oily and meaty food,

20:58.240 --> 20:59.590
but you don't like it.

21:00.790 --> 21:01.850
Yes, that's right.

21:02.510 --> 21:03.640
I did sports as a kid.

21:03.720 --> 21:05.350
My family made me eat meat every day,

21:05.350 --> 21:06.480
so I got tired of it.

21:06.550 --> 21:07.720
You did sports?

21:08.640 --> 21:10.000
I trained in sprinting for a few years,

21:10.000 --> 21:11.930
but then I got injured and stopped.

21:12.400 --> 21:14.080
Although the injury wasn't serious,

21:14.080 --> 21:15.210
I didn't really have

21:15.240 --> 21:16.630
any interest in sports training,

21:16.630 --> 21:17.240
so I quit.

21:17.790 --> 21:18.880
After quitting sports,

21:18.880 --> 21:21.010
you could still go back to high school.

21:21.070 --> 21:22.470
Your grades must be good.

21:23.030 --> 21:24.030
I won't be modest.

21:24.300 --> 21:25.560
They really were good.

21:33.510 --> 21:34.640
Are you trying to say

21:35.160 --> 21:35.880
you envy me?

21:36.710 --> 21:37.840
Having a good family

21:38.270 --> 21:40.110
and being able to do whatever I want?

21:40.110 --> 21:41.770
It's actually not that great.

21:42.480 --> 21:43.610
I've come to realize

21:44.000 --> 21:45.240
that when life's easier,

21:45.240 --> 21:46.640
people lose their drive.

21:46.880 --> 21:47.880
Look at Wei and me.

21:48.270 --> 21:50.200
We seem capable of doing anything,

21:50.640 --> 21:52.700
but we're not excellent at anything.

21:53.590 --> 21:54.160
Then

21:54.160 --> 21:56.360
why don't you find something to pursue?

21:59.590 --> 22:00.990
I haven't figured it out.

22:01.270 --> 22:02.240
And I lack

22:02.440 --> 22:04.370
the motivation to make a decision.

22:05.480 --> 22:06.740
The first day I met you,

22:07.160 --> 22:08.290
you had this spirit—

22:08.590 --> 22:09.880
something I don't have.

22:09.880 --> 22:11.810
That's why I'm so attracted to you.

22:13.070 --> 22:14.680
When you first met me...

22:24.480 --> 22:26.280
Actually, not long before that,

22:26.800 --> 22:28.210
I was a hopeless person.

22:30.110 --> 22:32.090
You were just in a desperate situation.

22:32.090 --> 22:33.480
If you were truly hopeless,

22:33.480 --> 22:35.510
you wouldn't have been the way I saw you.

22:35.510 --> 22:36.240
Ms. Xiaolan.

22:37.240 --> 22:39.350
Everyone faces difficulties

22:40.000 --> 22:40.860
and hardships.

22:41.350 --> 22:42.030
But you

22:42.550 --> 22:43.310
showed me

22:43.310 --> 22:44.640
such vibrant vitality.

22:47.920 --> 22:49.320
I'm not as good as you say,

22:49.480 --> 22:50.350
but

22:51.160 --> 22:52.890
I'm certainly not bad, either.

22:54.540 --> 22:55.800
Take your time eating.

22:56.110 --> 22:57.970
I'm going to pursue my dreams now.

22:58.750 --> 22:59.480
Ms. Xiaolan.

23:00.240 --> 23:00.900
Xiaolan...

23:05.070 --> 23:05.960
Wait for me!

23:06.000 --> 23:07.730
I'll finish eating right away.

23:10.880 --> 23:12.010
Wait for me a moment.

23:21.270 --> 23:22.530
Let me get you ten more.

23:22.790 --> 23:23.120
Good.

23:26.640 --> 23:27.440
You bought twenty,

23:27.440 --> 23:29.240
I'll give you some green onions.

23:29.270 --> 23:29.790
Okay.

23:29.790 --> 23:31.160
Fried duck eggs
with green onions are delicious.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.200
Try it when you get home.

23:32.200 --> 23:33.400
Alright, I'll try it.

23:33.550 --> 23:33.960
Here's the money.

23:33.960 --> 23:34.790
Okay, thank you.

23:34.790 --> 23:35.250
Thanks.

23:37.640 --> 23:38.310
Popsicle!

23:39.030 --> 23:39.720
Popsicle!

23:40.160 --> 23:41.020
Your lunchbox.

23:42.680 --> 23:43.280
Thank you.

23:43.510 --> 23:45.240
The dumplings were delicious.

23:45.750 --> 23:47.790
Buy duck eggs and get scallions free?

23:47.790 --> 23:49.310
You're really good at business.

23:49.310 --> 23:50.240
That's nothing,

23:50.240 --> 23:51.920
just a basic sales strategy.

23:52.590 --> 23:53.590
Sales strategy?

23:54.750 --> 23:55.950
You've studied this?

23:57.590 --> 23:58.920
I've read a bit about it.

24:00.880 --> 24:01.750
Don't stand here.

24:01.750 --> 24:02.440
You're blocking my business.

24:02.440 --> 24:03.100
Move aside.

24:03.600 --> 24:04.200
Do you want to buy duck eggs?

24:04.200 --> 24:05.550
How much are these duck eggs?

24:05.550 --> 24:06.070
Take a look.

24:06.070 --> 24:07.130
Duck eggs for sale!

24:08.030 --> 24:09.640
The more you buy, the better deal you get.

24:09.640 --> 24:11.900
Buy twenty
and you get green onions free.

24:12.240 --> 24:13.310
Let me think about it.

24:13.310 --> 24:13.960
Alright.

24:17.480 --> 24:18.350
If you're interested

24:18.350 --> 24:19.280
in making money,

24:19.400 --> 24:20.200
I can introduce you to some people

24:20.200 --> 24:21.060
-I know—
-Stop.

24:22.270 --> 24:23.270
Yes, that's right.

24:23.270 --> 24:24.880
I am interested in making money,

24:24.880 --> 24:26.440
but I don't need anyone's help.

24:26.440 --> 24:27.440
I can do it myself.

24:28.640 --> 24:30.100
Just by selling duck eggs?

24:32.270 --> 24:34.790
Selling duck eggs
was a form of primitive accumulation

24:34.790 --> 24:36.180
and also a way to test the waters.

24:36.180 --> 24:38.030
I'm not very familiar with this place.

24:38.030 --> 24:40.240
I need to research the market first

24:40.240 --> 24:42.100
before changing the sales model.

24:42.310 --> 24:43.770
Once I have the equipment,

24:43.790 --> 24:44.890
I can set up a stall

24:44.920 --> 24:47.320
and sell egg pancakes and hamburgers here.

24:47.360 --> 24:48.890
You're from the city, right?

24:48.890 --> 24:50.440
Then you must
have seen Western restaurants

24:50.440 --> 24:51.480
and eaten hamburgers.

24:51.480 --> 24:52.720
If

24:52.750 --> 24:54.200
I sell egg burgers here,

24:54.270 --> 24:55.870
would people here like them?

24:57.270 --> 24:58.790
I know all the words

24:59.310 --> 25:00.110
you said,

25:01.030 --> 25:01.880
but when you put them together,

25:01.880 --> 25:03.200
I don't understand what you mean.

25:03.200 --> 25:05.590
P-primitive accumulation?

25:06.550 --> 25:07.480
Test the waters?

25:09.030 --> 25:10.880
I've never heard of these things.

25:10.880 --> 25:11.440
Where did you learn

25:11.440 --> 25:12.480
all of this?

25:12.920 --> 25:14.510
I have eaten hamburgers before,

25:14.510 --> 25:16.270
but I've never heard of egg burgers.

25:16.270 --> 25:17.870
I'd actually like to try one.

25:18.240 --> 25:19.110
Ms. Xiaolan,

25:19.900 --> 25:22.030
you really are different from others.

25:22.480 --> 25:23.720
Clothes for sale!

25:23.880 --> 25:24.920
Clothes!

25:25.880 --> 25:27.030
This fabric is really good.

25:27.030 --> 25:27.790
It's polyester fabric.

25:27.790 --> 25:28.510
What are you looking at?

25:28.510 --> 25:29.110
They are really cool.

25:29.110 --> 25:30.400
Do you want to buy clothes?

25:30.400 --> 25:31.440
They look really nice.

25:31.440 --> 25:32.350
No, not buy—

25:32.510 --> 25:33.200
sell.

25:33.680 --> 25:34.550
Selling clothes definitely

25:34.550 --> 25:36.720
makes more money
than selling farm products.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.440
But I don't have enough capital now.

25:38.440 --> 25:39.680
If I were selling them,

25:39.680 --> 25:41.740
I'd definitely sell better than her.

25:46.480 --> 25:47.880
Why haven't you left yet?

25:48.400 --> 25:49.030
I want to buy...

25:49.030 --> 25:50.720
You heard what those thugs said yesterday,

25:50.720 --> 25:51.550
didn't you?

25:52.510 --> 25:53.270
I might actually be

25:53.270 --> 25:55.000
different from what you think.

25:57.480 --> 25:58.590
I don't judge people

25:58.590 --> 25:59.520
based on rumors.

26:00.080 --> 26:01.480
I only believe what I see.

26:01.960 --> 26:02.960
If I have doubts,

26:03.310 --> 26:04.240
I will research them myself,

26:04.240 --> 26:07.100
and I won't just make assumptions
based on hearsay.

26:08.680 --> 26:11.480
Unfortunately, there are too few people
like you.

26:11.550 --> 26:13.410
Some people don't just hate me...

26:13.920 --> 26:15.250
They want to destroy me.

26:18.870 --> 26:20.980
Those "winged" rumors

26:21.440 --> 26:22.640
must come from

26:22.660 --> 26:24.190
my "golden phoenix" cousin

26:24.270 --> 26:25.330
and her boyfriend.

26:25.880 --> 26:28.480
Can't even keep
one Xia Xiaolan under control.

26:29.070 --> 26:29.640
Ziyu.

26:35.270 --> 26:35.960
Jianhua.

26:37.070 --> 26:37.870
What's wrong?

26:38.550 --> 26:39.640
You look unhappy.

26:39.640 --> 26:40.270
No,

26:40.480 --> 26:41.410
I'm quite happy.

26:41.960 --> 26:43.110
Let's go to the dining hall.

26:43.110 --> 26:43.550
Okay.

26:43.720 --> 26:44.250
Let's go.

26:47.150 --> 26:48.780
I don't care what tricks they're up to.

26:47.720 --> 26:53.150
[State-Run Restaurant]

26:49.640 --> 26:50.400
However,

26:50.720 --> 26:52.270
being constantly followed by rumors

26:52.270 --> 26:53.330
is quite annoying.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.170
Alright.

26:55.310 --> 26:56.720
If you need help,

26:56.750 --> 26:58.030
I can actually help you find...

26:58.030 --> 26:58.490
No need.

26:59.560 --> 27:00.540
Actually, I won't be staying here

27:00.540 --> 27:01.580
for too long.

27:01.790 --> 27:03.550
I don't really mind these things.

27:03.550 --> 27:04.160
And even if

27:04.160 --> 27:05.640
I really need to resolve it,

27:05.640 --> 27:06.900
I can handle it myself.

27:07.590 --> 27:09.550
I don't want to owe you any more favors.

27:09.550 --> 27:10.550
There you two are!

27:10.960 --> 27:11.480
Good.

27:11.830 --> 27:12.350
Sir,

27:12.720 --> 27:14.640
I already had dumplings this morning.

27:14.640 --> 27:15.440
No need to treat me to lunch.

27:15.440 --> 27:16.240
That won't do.

27:16.310 --> 27:17.070
That's different.

27:17.070 --> 27:18.800
I've already ordered the dishes.

27:18.800 --> 27:20.000
We must show you our appreciation.

27:20.000 --> 27:20.720
Come on in.

27:21.030 --> 27:21.510
Let's go.

27:21.510 --> 27:22.130
Well, thank you, sir.

27:22.130 --> 27:22.760
Come on.

27:28.960 --> 27:30.240
All the dishes are here.

27:30.240 --> 27:30.790
Sir.

27:31.750 --> 27:33.070
Fish filets in hot chili oil,

27:33.070 --> 27:34.200
fish head with chopped chili,

27:34.200 --> 27:35.750
fish ball soup, and fried fish fillets.

27:35.750 --> 27:37.070
It's one fish prepared in four ways!

27:37.070 --> 27:38.930
You've ordered a brilliant meal.

27:39.270 --> 27:41.030
This is... a black carp?

27:41.310 --> 27:43.110
It must be about 17 or 18 catties.

27:43.880 --> 27:45.030
Mr. Zhou is

27:45.030 --> 27:46.360
really knowledgeable.

27:46.680 --> 27:47.680
You can even tell

27:47.680 --> 27:48.940
that it's a black carp.

27:49.000 --> 27:50.240
Come on, eat up.

27:53.240 --> 27:53.970
Here you are.

27:58.820 --> 27:59.780
Here, Xiaolan.

28:02.480 --> 28:03.270
Use this one.

28:04.350 --> 28:05.000
Eat up.

28:07.790 --> 28:09.260
I'd like to toast you two

28:09.350 --> 28:10.750
for saving Xiaolan.

28:11.550 --> 28:12.550
Don't mention it.

28:12.720 --> 28:14.180
You can call me Zhou Cheng.

28:14.350 --> 28:15.470
Or Cheng is fine, too.

28:15.470 --> 28:16.730
We'd like to toast you.

28:18.350 --> 28:19.790
Xiaolan and I hit it off when we

28:19.790 --> 28:20.480
first met.

28:25.480 --> 28:26.790
You're still so young.

28:26.790 --> 28:28.390
Don't speak so frivolously.

28:28.750 --> 28:31.350
What do you mean
you hit it off when you just met?

28:31.590 --> 28:32.680
We're treating you to this meal

28:32.680 --> 28:34.220
to thank you for saving her life.

28:34.220 --> 28:35.050
That's all.

28:36.030 --> 28:37.440
You must mind your words.

28:38.480 --> 28:39.880
I was being impertinent.

28:40.000 --> 28:41.060
This is my apology.

28:45.530 --> 28:46.450
I'm so sorry

28:46.480 --> 28:47.740
for the misunderstanding.

28:47.740 --> 28:48.730
I didn't mean anything else

28:48.730 --> 28:49.640
by saying that.

28:50.000 --> 28:51.530
I just wanted to let you know

28:51.920 --> 28:52.990
that I'm sincere

28:53.480 --> 28:55.410
about being friends with Xiaolan.

29:05.030 --> 29:05.690
Zhou Cheng,

29:05.920 --> 29:07.480
since you're being so honest,

29:07.480 --> 29:08.940
I'll just cut to the chase.

29:09.270 --> 29:10.530
I admit you're not bad.

29:10.760 --> 29:11.890
But right now,

29:11.920 --> 29:13.350
I don't have time for this.

29:13.350 --> 29:15.280
I have more important things to do.

29:18.110 --> 29:19.640
I understand what you mean.

29:20.160 --> 29:21.020
We've just met.

29:21.790 --> 29:22.850
I'm not rushing it.

29:23.200 --> 29:25.350
And you don't need
to feel pressured, either.

29:25.350 --> 29:26.270
Let's interact

29:26.790 --> 29:27.350
normally,

29:27.350 --> 29:28.410
just like friends.

29:29.270 --> 29:30.000
Try the fish.

29:31.690 --> 29:32.340
Have some fish, sir.

29:32.340 --> 29:33.470
Good that you got it.

29:35.720 --> 29:36.680
I have to admit

29:37.030 --> 29:38.760
that under any circumstances,

29:39.000 --> 29:40.550
this kind of youthful enthusiasm is

29:40.550 --> 29:41.550
always touching.

29:42.680 --> 29:44.480
But touching as it may be,

29:44.960 --> 29:46.560
this isn't my life after all.

29:46.920 --> 29:47.830
Sooner or later, I'll return

29:47.830 --> 29:49.030
to the world I'm from.

29:49.440 --> 29:51.440
Why form an additional attachment?

30:09.230 --> 30:10.510
Hey, man.

30:10.750 --> 30:11.480
We're the ones

30:11.480 --> 30:13.140
who said to treat you to a meal.

30:13.400 --> 30:14.730
Why did you pay the bill?

30:15.640 --> 30:17.170
It doesn't matter who paid.

30:17.350 --> 30:17.880
The point is

30:17.880 --> 30:19.480
that we all enjoyed the meal.

30:22.480 --> 30:23.240
Are you two

30:23.440 --> 30:24.350
going anywhere else?

30:24.350 --> 30:25.550
We can give you a ride.

30:25.670 --> 30:26.300
Don't bother.

30:26.300 --> 30:27.640
We've taken up your whole day already.

30:27.640 --> 30:28.750
Just go ahead with your business.

30:28.750 --> 30:29.550
We'll be fine.

30:32.430 --> 30:32.960
Alright.

30:33.160 --> 30:34.400
Take care on your way.

30:34.640 --> 30:36.290
We'll be staying here for two more days.

30:36.290 --> 30:37.690
If you come into town for anything,

30:37.690 --> 30:39.550
you can find us at the guesthouse.

30:41.070 --> 30:41.680
Well,

30:41.920 --> 30:43.120
we'll take our leave.

30:59.440 --> 30:59.880
Cheng,

31:00.310 --> 31:02.200
you didn't go to the police station today.

31:02.200 --> 31:04.240
What those three thugs said is so nasty

31:04.240 --> 31:05.310
that I don't even want to repeat it.

31:05.310 --> 31:06.770
Then just don't repeat it.

31:07.990 --> 31:08.400
Wei.

31:09.590 --> 31:11.050
Do you think I'm handsome?

31:11.590 --> 31:12.440
Yes, of course!

31:12.440 --> 31:13.350
Back in the compound when we were kids,

31:13.350 --> 31:14.950
all the girls were after you.

31:14.980 --> 31:15.780
Then am I rich?

31:17.100 --> 31:18.960
Since I'm both handsome and rich,

31:19.240 --> 31:21.480
and I've openly expressed
my admiration for her,

31:21.480 --> 31:22.440
if she were really

31:22.440 --> 31:23.110
as terrible

31:23.110 --> 31:24.170
as that rogue said,

31:24.350 --> 31:25.700
why would she turn down someone

31:25.700 --> 31:27.500
with such good conditions as me?

31:30.240 --> 31:32.370
She'll be your sister-in-law one day.

31:32.880 --> 31:33.340
Let's go

31:33.700 --> 31:34.500
do something.

31:35.550 --> 31:37.750
Weren't we going back
to rest at the guesthouse?

31:37.750 --> 31:39.240
These two must be

31:39.590 --> 31:40.790
smugglers

31:41.550 --> 31:42.950
doing illegal business.

31:43.730 --> 31:44.650
They might

31:44.680 --> 31:46.080
lose everything one day.

31:46.160 --> 31:47.030
You can't just be fooled

31:47.030 --> 31:48.630
by this man's handsome looks

31:48.750 --> 31:50.480
and sweet talk.

31:52.400 --> 31:53.730
How do you know all this?

31:54.590 --> 31:56.110
Aren't you a mason?

31:57.000 --> 31:59.200
How do you know so much about smuggling?

32:01.310 --> 32:02.680
Because I'm smart.

32:05.550 --> 32:07.400
Let's s-stop talking about those two.

32:07.400 --> 32:09.400
Let's talk about those three thugs.

32:09.660 --> 32:11.270
They're now insisting

32:11.310 --> 32:12.830
that they only went to hurt you

32:12.830 --> 32:13.960
after hearing those rumors.

32:13.960 --> 32:15.750
They'll definitely get a heavy sentence.

32:15.750 --> 32:17.000
At your age,

32:17.200 --> 32:18.790
reputation matters so much.

32:18.790 --> 32:19.240
These days...

32:19.240 --> 32:21.240
P-Please don't do anything for now.

32:21.480 --> 32:22.680
Let me think about it.

32:23.260 --> 32:23.880
Hello, excuse me.

32:23.880 --> 32:24.880
I'd like to ask about someone.

32:24.880 --> 32:26.270
Do you know Zhang Erlai?

32:27.030 --> 32:28.370
He's just a hideous scoundrel.

32:28.370 --> 32:28.920
He's messed

32:28.920 --> 32:29.880
with many young girls

32:29.880 --> 32:31.030
from several villages around here.

32:31.030 --> 32:31.750
Thank you, ma'am.

32:31.750 --> 32:32.110
Sir,

32:32.200 --> 32:33.240
could I ask you about someone?

32:33.240 --> 32:34.640
Do you know Zhang Erlai?

32:34.640 --> 32:36.640
I'm busy and don't have time for you.

32:41.480 --> 32:42.000
Cheng,

32:42.960 --> 32:43.550
see?

32:44.000 --> 32:45.480
We've been hearing all day about how she

32:45.480 --> 32:46.640
failed to seduce her cousin's husband

32:46.640 --> 32:47.720
and turned to mess

32:47.720 --> 32:48.270
with that rascal.

32:48.270 --> 32:48.870
Screw you.

32:50.310 --> 32:51.830
Look, even if I believe

32:51.830 --> 32:53.160
that Xia Xiaolan isn't
that kind of person,

32:53.160 --> 32:54.690
everyone here is saying it.

32:54.790 --> 32:55.400
Getting mixed up with her

32:55.400 --> 32:56.920
will surely bring you endless trouble.

32:56.920 --> 32:57.590
First of all,

32:57.590 --> 32:59.440
your family won't easily accept her.

32:59.440 --> 33:00.100
Look at you.

33:00.240 --> 33:01.040
You saved her,

33:01.350 --> 33:02.310
confessed your love in public,

33:02.310 --> 33:03.640
and showed off your wealth.

33:03.640 --> 33:04.110
But look at her.

33:04.110 --> 33:05.270
She's not interested at all.

33:05.270 --> 33:07.130
Just pack up and come home with me.

33:07.350 --> 33:08.280
I'm not leaving.

33:08.880 --> 33:09.790
Let's go

33:09.850 --> 33:10.680
to Shipozi Village

33:10.680 --> 33:11.540
they mentioned

33:11.960 --> 33:13.160
and meet Zhang Erlai.

33:15.460 --> 33:17.520
You've been bewitched by that woman.

33:32.590 --> 33:33.520
This alarm clock

33:34.240 --> 33:35.200
rings whenever

33:35.200 --> 33:36.350
you want it to.

33:56.240 --> 33:56.790
Xiaolan,

33:57.240 --> 33:59.100
your alarm clock rings so loudly.

34:00.480 --> 34:00.940
Auntie,

34:01.110 --> 34:02.070
this is the money I earned

34:02.070 --> 34:03.210
selling duck eggs in the past few days.

34:03.210 --> 34:03.830
Please take it

34:03.830 --> 34:05.030
for our food expense.

34:05.590 --> 34:06.200
Well...

34:06.200 --> 34:06.660
Take it.

34:07.160 --> 34:07.490
Oh...

34:07.720 --> 34:08.800
What's this for?

34:09.510 --> 34:11.110
You don't need to do this
while living at your uncle's house.

34:11.110 --> 34:11.880
We don't need your money.

34:11.880 --> 34:12.480
That's right.

34:12.480 --> 34:13.670
I know you don't need it,

34:13.670 --> 34:15.469
but if you don't take this money,

34:15.670 --> 34:16.440
I'd feel bad

34:16.440 --> 34:17.840
staying here any longer.

34:18.110 --> 34:19.590
Look at this girl...

34:20.110 --> 34:20.969
How about this?

34:21.070 --> 34:21.760
Your auntie will

34:21.760 --> 34:23.090
keep this money for you,

34:23.150 --> 34:24.590
and when you need it,

34:24.710 --> 34:25.760
she'll return it to you.

34:25.760 --> 34:27.400
Yeah, good girl.

34:32.960 --> 34:34.030
What's wrong?

34:35.440 --> 34:36.110
Nothing.

34:36.590 --> 34:37.190
It's just

34:37.190 --> 34:39.050
that I didn't get many eggs today.

34:40.760 --> 34:42.400
Anyone can tell your sadness
from your face.

34:42.400 --> 34:43.730
What's really going on?

34:44.590 --> 34:45.650
The villagers said

34:46.000 --> 34:47.460
duck eggs are profitable.

34:47.920 --> 34:49.280
They want to sell them themselves

34:49.280 --> 34:50.540
and can't give me many.

34:52.000 --> 34:53.400
I should have told you earlier.

34:53.400 --> 34:54.840
I actually expected this.

34:54.840 --> 34:55.969
People always fight

34:56.110 --> 34:57.280
for jobs that pay well.

34:57.280 --> 34:59.140
So what if we didn't get duck eggs?

35:03.590 --> 35:04.110
Fen?

35:06.230 --> 35:07.290
What's wrong, Fen?

35:07.670 --> 35:08.710
Why are you crying?

35:08.710 --> 35:09.840
What are you crying for?

35:09.840 --> 35:10.360
Fen,

35:10.480 --> 35:11.280
don't cry.

35:11.760 --> 35:12.920
They were talking

35:13.440 --> 35:14.550
about Xiaolan.

35:15.600 --> 35:16.360
What did they say?

35:16.360 --> 35:17.360
What did they say?

35:18.880 --> 35:19.810
They said she...

35:25.030 --> 35:26.280
Who's got nothing better to do

35:26.280 --> 35:27.440
than gossip around here?

35:27.440 --> 35:28.000
What are you doing?

35:28.000 --> 35:29.110
Get your ass over here!

35:29.110 --> 35:31.010
I'll rip that tongue
right out of your big mouth!

35:31.010 --> 35:31.480
That's enough.

35:31.480 --> 35:32.410
How despicable,

35:32.510 --> 35:34.150
talking rubbish about our innocent girl!

35:34.150 --> 35:35.410
You shameless people!

35:35.590 --> 35:36.670
Enough, Fengmei. Stop it...

35:36.670 --> 35:37.400
You think our family has no one

35:37.400 --> 35:38.110
to stand up for her?

35:38.110 --> 35:38.960
Stop shouting!

35:38.960 --> 35:40.220
Xiaolan is still here!

35:42.110 --> 35:43.310
And you, stop crying.

35:43.440 --> 35:43.880
Your tears

35:43.880 --> 35:44.960
won't solve anything!

35:44.960 --> 35:45.630
Those damn bastards are

35:45.630 --> 35:47.830
spreading rumors and causing trouble.

35:48.030 --> 35:48.630
I know

35:49.230 --> 35:50.760
it must be that Zhang Erlai!

35:51.240 --> 35:52.080
Zhang Erlai is

35:52.110 --> 35:53.110
a filthy hooligan,

35:53.110 --> 35:53.840
a scoundrel!

35:56.030 --> 35:58.360
I'm not the Xia Xiaolan they gossip about.

35:58.710 --> 36:00.240
These things can't hurt me.

36:01.230 --> 36:02.590
But they can hurt them,

36:03.550 --> 36:04.950
my unfamiliar "family."

36:05.480 --> 36:06.660
Don't let me see you!

36:06.800 --> 36:07.230
I'll beat you

36:07.230 --> 36:08.760
every single time I see you!

36:08.960 --> 36:10.480
What they're saying isn't true.

36:10.480 --> 36:11.940
Xiaolan, you are the best.

36:14.970 --> 36:16.000
See? He failed to get what he wanted,

36:16.000 --> 36:17.030
so he's spreading rumors here!

36:17.030 --> 36:17.630
All right,

36:18.070 --> 36:18.800
stop crying.

36:22.360 --> 36:23.090
Zhang Erlai,

36:23.590 --> 36:24.070
right?

36:32.710 --> 36:34.000
Zhang Erlai is

36:34.190 --> 36:36.070
always getting handsy.

36:36.220 --> 36:37.610
The women in Shipozi Village

36:37.610 --> 36:38.500
all avoid him.

36:40.400 --> 36:42.670
It's improper for me
to confront him directly.

36:42.670 --> 36:44.070
Could you help me find out

36:44.360 --> 36:46.000
if he has any hobbies

36:46.480 --> 36:47.810
or places he likes to go?

36:49.110 --> 36:50.310
You want to catch him?

36:53.030 --> 36:54.830
Words alone aren't solid proof.

36:55.230 --> 36:56.760
We must catch him in the act.

36:56.840 --> 36:57.920
Someone like him will strike

36:57.920 --> 36:59.520
whenever he gets the chance.

37:02.190 --> 37:03.510
I've already spoken with people

37:03.510 --> 37:04.800
in his village and told them

37:04.800 --> 37:06.260
to keep an eye on him for me.

37:08.400 --> 37:08.880
Ma'am.

37:09.130 --> 37:09.730
Oh, right,

37:09.970 --> 37:10.960
they said recently,

37:10.960 --> 37:11.800
someone else was also

37:11.800 --> 37:13.260
asking about Zhang Erlai.

37:13.670 --> 37:16.030
This guy seems to have offended
quite a few people.

37:16.030 --> 37:17.490
Everyone wants to get him.

37:17.590 --> 37:18.390
Someone else?

37:20.000 --> 37:20.880
Looks like Zhang Erlai

37:20.880 --> 37:21.880
lives up to his name.

37:21.880 --> 37:22.940
He's no good at all.

37:23.920 --> 37:24.920
Hello, sir.

37:25.250 --> 37:26.130
Excuse me,

37:26.150 --> 37:27.550
do you know Zhang Erlai?

37:29.550 --> 37:30.080
Get lost!

37:31.910 --> 37:32.400
Don't run!

37:32.400 --> 37:33.070
Kids, come here.

37:33.070 --> 37:33.840
I must catch him.

37:33.840 --> 37:35.190
I have a question for you.

37:35.190 --> 37:35.880
If you

37:35.880 --> 37:36.880
know anything,

37:37.070 --> 37:38.760
you'll get a candy.

37:39.030 --> 37:40.400
Okay! Me!

37:40.420 --> 37:42.150
Who knows Zhang Erlai?

37:42.280 --> 37:43.280
I know! I know him.

37:43.480 --> 37:45.510
Xiaoling's sister stays at home all day,

37:45.510 --> 37:46.710
cursing Zhang Erlai.

37:46.800 --> 37:47.250
Yeah.

37:47.280 --> 37:47.630
Dan'er,

37:47.630 --> 37:48.480
didn't he once

37:48.480 --> 37:49.480
grope your sister, too?

37:49.480 --> 37:50.510
He groped your sister!

37:50.510 --> 37:51.570
It was your sister!

38:39.330 --> 38:40.670
[To Xia Xiaolan]

38:52.980 --> 38:55.500
[See you at the usual spot. From Jianhua.]

39:09.150 --> 39:11.360
The handwriting is completely different.

39:11.360 --> 39:12.400
She fell

39:12.400 --> 39:13.730
for such a clumsy trick.

39:13.960 --> 39:15.360
What a silly girl.

39:20.380 --> 39:21.580
What's wrong, Cheng?

39:21.630 --> 39:23.490
This Zhang Erlai has gone too far.

39:23.760 --> 39:25.760
Xia Xiaolan must have been wronged.

39:26.480 --> 39:27.400
Visit two more houses

39:27.400 --> 39:28.380
and send all this evidence

39:28.380 --> 39:29.640
to the police station.

39:31.000 --> 39:32.030
W-Where are you going?

39:32.030 --> 39:33.490
Aren't you coming with me?

39:33.510 --> 39:34.920
I'm going to help your sister-in-law

39:34.920 --> 39:36.030
sell duck eggs.

39:38.960 --> 39:39.760
Cheng!

39:41.280 --> 39:42.080
Xiaolan!

39:43.360 --> 39:44.630
Are you still buying duck eggs?

39:44.630 --> 39:45.070
Yes.

39:45.800 --> 39:46.860
I have twelve here.

39:47.150 --> 39:47.960
I have eight.

39:48.110 --> 39:49.370
I'll give you 70 cents.

39:49.480 --> 39:50.150
And 50 cents for you.

39:50.150 --> 39:50.920
Okay.

39:50.920 --> 39:51.400
Put them in here.

39:51.400 --> 39:52.230
I'll get you money.

39:52.230 --> 39:52.560
Okay.

39:52.920 --> 39:53.980
I'll put them here.

39:58.150 --> 39:59.030
Here's yours.

40:00.030 --> 40:00.630
Thank you.

40:01.840 --> 40:02.440
And yours.

40:02.550 --> 40:04.030
Okay, thanks.

40:04.630 --> 40:05.920
Are these duck eggs for sale?

40:05.920 --> 40:06.320
Yes.

40:08.800 --> 40:09.440
Xiaolan,

40:09.840 --> 40:10.640
good morning.

40:10.960 --> 40:11.890
Why are you here?

40:12.670 --> 40:14.870
I still have some unfinished business.

40:17.710 --> 40:19.630
Why so few duck eggs today?

40:20.920 --> 40:21.670
The villagers

40:21.670 --> 40:23.110
heard that selling duck eggs makes money,

40:23.110 --> 40:24.790
so few would sell them to me now.

40:24.790 --> 40:26.230
They all want to make money themselves.

40:26.230 --> 40:27.280
But it doesn't matter.

40:27.280 --> 40:28.440
I don't plan

40:28.440 --> 40:30.240
to stay in this business anyway.

40:30.960 --> 40:32.160
What will you do next?

40:32.550 --> 40:33.480
Next?

40:34.030 --> 40:35.690
I haven't thought about that.

40:36.590 --> 40:38.280
Since there's no business today anyway,

40:38.280 --> 40:38.740
come on,

40:39.000 --> 40:40.860
I'll show you some rural scenery.

40:42.400 --> 40:43.480
Handle them gently.

40:43.480 --> 40:44.440
You'll have to pay if they break.

40:44.440 --> 40:44.840
Okay.

40:59.700 --> 41:01.630
That's the one from Dahe Village, right?

41:01.630 --> 41:02.630
I think so.

41:03.230 --> 41:04.070
That's her.

41:04.360 --> 41:06.590
-Why did she get mixed up with Zhang Erlai?
-That's how rumors spread.

41:06.590 --> 41:07.550
Exactly.

41:08.440 --> 41:09.800
It's the same in the city.

41:09.800 --> 41:10.590
Some things

41:10.590 --> 41:12.400
get distorted when passed around.

41:12.400 --> 41:14.260
It's hard to keep everyone quiet.

41:17.480 --> 41:18.340
You scoundrel!

41:18.590 --> 41:19.920
You have nowhere to escape!

41:19.920 --> 41:21.250
Isn't that Zhang Erlai?

41:21.360 --> 41:22.090
Zhang Erlai!

41:22.280 --> 41:23.280
Why are you here?

41:23.440 --> 41:25.480
You harass young girls
in the village every day!

41:25.480 --> 41:26.880
You disgusting pervert!

41:27.110 --> 41:28.640
Why is your uncle here, too?

41:29.230 --> 41:30.230
Since we're here,

41:30.510 --> 41:31.710
let's watch the show.

41:31.720 --> 41:32.450
Zhang Erlai,

41:32.750 --> 41:33.480
you bullied Xia Xiaolan

41:33.480 --> 41:35.280
from Dahe Village the other day.

41:35.390 --> 41:36.630
This person should've called the police

41:36.630 --> 41:37.840
and sent you to the police station!

41:37.840 --> 41:38.510
Yes, that's right.

41:38.510 --> 41:39.920
Call the police to catch him.

41:39.920 --> 41:41.110
Don't talk nonsense.

41:41.110 --> 41:42.880
There's nothing
between Xia Xiaolan and me.

41:42.880 --> 41:43.760
If you keep making things up,

41:43.760 --> 41:45.440
I'll tell the police to arrest you!

41:45.440 --> 41:47.040
Did you see it with your eyes?

41:47.150 --> 41:48.750
Dare you come to confront me?

41:49.160 --> 41:50.190
He's still denying it!

41:50.190 --> 41:50.840
He thinks he's right!

41:50.840 --> 41:53.640
-That's horrendous!
-Let me confront you myself.

41:54.800 --> 41:55.530
Zhang Erlai,

41:56.550 --> 41:57.610
do you remember me?

41:58.480 --> 41:59.400
Xia Xiaolan?

41:59.800 --> 42:00.760
Repeat what you

42:00.760 --> 42:01.440
just said.

42:01.920 --> 42:02.440
I...

42:02.770 --> 42:04.090
What did I say?

42:04.150 --> 42:04.670
Speak!

42:05.150 --> 42:06.760
Weren't you quite talkative just now?

42:06.760 --> 42:07.490
Say it again!

42:08.550 --> 42:10.080
Be it in the past or present,

42:10.630 --> 42:11.800
when misunderstood

42:11.920 --> 42:12.720
or slandered,

42:12.800 --> 42:14.670
many people only choose to run away.

42:14.670 --> 42:16.110
But when you hide from rumors,

42:16.110 --> 42:17.910
the rumors will chase after you.

42:17.960 --> 42:19.890
There's only one way to end rumors.

42:20.260 --> 42:20.810
And that is

42:20.810 --> 42:22.270
to confront them head-on.

42:23.030 --> 42:24.030
Fine, I'll speak!

42:24.590 --> 42:26.230
I'm not that kind of perverted person.

42:26.230 --> 42:28.200
And I've never done that filthy thing!

42:28.200 --> 42:29.450
Oh... How shameless!

42:29.480 --> 42:30.440
Look how nervous he appears!

42:30.440 --> 42:31.300
Of course he's nervous.

42:31.300 --> 42:32.560
He's obviously lying.

42:32.590 --> 42:33.480
Zhang Erlai and I

42:33.480 --> 42:35.230
have met only three times in total.

42:35.230 --> 42:36.360
The first two times,

42:36.810 --> 42:38.330
you verbally flirted

42:38.360 --> 42:39.360
and got handsy with me.

42:39.360 --> 42:40.670
I scolded you and drove you away.

42:40.670 --> 42:41.360
Later, I don't know

42:41.360 --> 42:42.710
who left you a note,

42:42.840 --> 42:44.440
claiming that I fell for you.

42:45.110 --> 42:46.190
Who'd possibly

42:46.260 --> 42:47.400
fall for someone like him?

42:47.400 --> 42:47.930
Exactly!

42:48.300 --> 42:50.230
Someone really did leave me a note.

42:50.510 --> 42:51.240
Zhang Erlai!

42:51.300 --> 42:52.760
That doesn't make any sense.

42:52.760 --> 42:53.670
You just believed

42:53.670 --> 42:54.630
some random note?

42:54.630 --> 42:55.360
That girl is

42:55.360 --> 42:56.360
so capable and competent.

42:56.360 --> 42:57.590
She'd have to be blind to like you.

42:57.590 --> 42:58.190
Exactly.

42:58.670 --> 42:59.800
I was just thinking,

42:59.960 --> 43:00.710
"What if it's true?"

43:00.710 --> 43:01.550
Seriously?

43:01.550 --> 43:02.320
Who gave you that note?

43:02.320 --> 43:03.360
How ridiculous! Look at yourself.

43:03.360 --> 43:03.960
So hilarious.

43:03.960 --> 43:05.400
How would I know who left me that?

43:05.400 --> 43:06.590
When I got home,

43:06.840 --> 43:08.110
the note was right under my door.

43:08.110 --> 43:09.590
I received a similar note,

43:10.550 --> 43:11.960
but it wasn't about you.

43:12.550 --> 43:13.610
After meeting you,

43:13.800 --> 43:15.930
I immediately made my position clear.

43:16.070 --> 43:17.360
I also showed you the note.

43:17.360 --> 43:18.150
You knew perfectly well

43:18.150 --> 43:19.360
that I was tricked into coming.

43:19.360 --> 43:21.160
Yet you still got handsy with me.

43:21.630 --> 43:22.800
I tried everything to get rid of you,

43:22.800 --> 43:24.030
and you, embarrassed and furious,

43:24.030 --> 43:24.960
spread rumors everywhere,

43:24.960 --> 43:26.490
saying that we were dating.

43:26.630 --> 43:27.590
How can a young woman like you

43:27.590 --> 43:28.520
be so shameless?

43:28.920 --> 43:29.960
We're in front of so many people.

43:29.960 --> 43:30.630
How can you eagerly talk about

43:30.630 --> 43:31.510
such embarrassing things?

43:31.510 --> 43:33.110
Why should I be embarrassed?

43:33.360 --> 43:34.550
If I didn't speak up,

43:34.760 --> 43:35.820
people might think

43:35.840 --> 43:37.440
I was admitting it silently out of shame.

43:37.440 --> 43:38.230
Should I let

43:38.230 --> 43:39.150
a rogue like you

43:39.380 --> 43:39.920
and all those

43:39.920 --> 43:41.000
malicious rumors

43:41.030 --> 43:42.000
belittle me?

43:42.110 --> 43:42.710
-You're right!
-Exactly.

43:42.710 --> 43:44.000
Should I let someone like you,

43:44.000 --> 43:45.400
who spreads rumors everywhere,

43:45.400 --> 43:46.510
continue doing evil,

43:46.510 --> 43:47.110
and let someone like me,

43:47.110 --> 43:48.320
a completely innocent victim,

43:48.320 --> 43:49.680
live in shame and fear?

43:50.110 --> 43:50.840
On what grounds?
